      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=ktukyo130u]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ktukyo130u]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=usc20mh3o9]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=usc20mh3o9]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=n8o4jymx01]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=n8o4jymx01]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=h8v5mtqxm6]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=h8v5mtqxm6]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=hqm8b01as0]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=hqm8b01as0]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=zfj6nnbsg2]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=zfj6nnbsg2]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=nme55ine42]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nme55ine42]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=dnzj951pqv]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=dnzj951pqv]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ftudt0w5hx]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ftudt0w5hx]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"shading_learingPath_banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725568341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=320\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599654499/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725568341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"714\" data-width=\"1695\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"636092435\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"shading_learingPath_banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599654499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"0f9879eb-35a8-4d22-bdcd-c1ae583320a9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725568341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=640 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725568341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=320 1x\" /></span><h1 id=\"MaterialXLama-StartHere\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"h8v5mtqxm6\">Start Here</span></strong></h1><p>A good place to start if you&rsquo;re new to Lama.</p><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/606076995/Lama+Fundamentals\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606076995\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaFundamentals.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/LamaFundamentals.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758193827176&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599654499/LamaFundamentals.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758193827176&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606077022\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaFundamentals.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599654499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"63dee249-3e4a-43c5-a433-8610ceabc1aa\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/LamaFundamentals.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758193827176&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/LamaFundamentals.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758193827176&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"n8o4jymx01\">Lama Fundamentals</span></strong><br />If you&rsquo;re new to Lama, this is a good place to start with our official Lama Fundamentals.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br /></p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"MaterialXLama-NextSteps\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"nme55ine42\">Next Steps</span></strong></h1><p>Now you&rsquo;ve learnt the basic building blocks of Lama, here are some more complex examples to work through.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/606240846/Lama+Metals\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606240846\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaMetal.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/LamaMetal.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758192245974&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599654499/LamaMetal.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758192245974&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606175276\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaMetal.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599654499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"661b6073-d7db-48cb-9632-eecd86d034e0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/LamaMetal.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758192245974&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/LamaMetal.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758192245974&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"hqm8b01as0\">Creating Lama Metals</span></strong><br />Here&rsquo;s how to make a metal material in Lama.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/606208122/Lama+Metallic+Workflow\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606208122\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Metallic_thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/Metallic_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438113315&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599654499/Metallic_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438113315&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"400\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"625541164\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Metallic_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599654499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"40aeb419-ab55-4838-be0e-f7db8c8ed396\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/Metallic_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438113315&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/Metallic_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438113315&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"zfj6nnbsg2\">Metallic workflow in Lama</span></strong><br />Using Lama with Metallic Maps?  Here&rsquo;s how!</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"MaterialXLama-FurtherLearning\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"dnzj951pqv\">Further Learning</span></strong></h1><p>Now you&rsquo;ve learnt the basic building blocks of Lama, here are some more complex examples to work through.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/632783516/Lama+Car+Paints\" data-linked-resource-id=\"632783516\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"carpaint_thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/carpaint_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760016952273&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599654499/carpaint_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760016952273&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"400\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"622788690\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"carpaint_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599654499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"2ce78c6f-ea78-4df5-8a26-b9c9160daa78\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/carpaint_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760016952273&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/carpaint_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760016952273&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ftudt0w5hx\">Creating Car paints in Lama</span></strong><br />Learn to make realistic metallic &amp; solid car paints in Lama.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/606175285/Lama+Layer+Storytelling\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606175285\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/Lama_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761486277643&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599654499/Lama_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761486277643&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"632848966\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599654499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"b73b3a09-dc92-483c-ac4c-1f75cce1a3e7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/Lama_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761486277643&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/Lama_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761486277643&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ktukyo130u\">Layers tell a Story</span></strong><br />An example of how layering Lama materials aids in giving your assets a story.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/657555758/Lama+Skin+Shading\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657555758\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"SSS.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/SSS.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762604317361&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599654499/SSS.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762604317361&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657424760\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"SSS.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599654499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"b1764b0e-cdb7-4f76-a9b8-12611f416e36\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/SSS.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762604317361&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654499/SSS.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762604317361&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"usc20mh3o9\">Lama Skin Shading</span></strong><br />Learn from Rassoul Edji on how he created his Samurai Lama skin shader.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\